## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Ruby 3.2+
- Rails 8+
- PostgreSQL (or SQLite for development)

### Setup

```bash
bin/setup    # Install dependencies and prepare databases
bin/dev      # Start all processes (web, css, solid_queue)
```

Your app will be running at **http://localhost:<%= options[:port] %>**.

