## Scripts

- `bin/setup` — Install dependencies and prepare databases
- `bin/dev` — Start all processes (web, css, solid_queue)

## Credentials

Edit credentials with:

```bash
bin/rails credentials:edit
```

Add backstage credentials for the jobs and errors dashboards:

```yaml
backstage:
  username: your_user
  password: your_password
```

## Maquina Ecosystem

### UI Components

[Maquina Components](https://maquina.app/documentation/components/) — a library of ERB partials, Tailwind CSS styles, and Stimulus controllers for building consistent, accessible UIs in Rails.

### AI Tools

Maquina provides a suite of AI-powered tools to accelerate your Rails development:

- **Rails MCP Server** — Model Context Protocol server for Rails applications
- **Rails Simplifier** — simplify and refine Rails code following 37signals patterns
- **Rails Upgrade Assistant** — comprehensive Rails upgrade reports and migration guides
- **Maquina UI Standards** — build consistent UIs using maquina_components
- **Neovim MCP Server** — MCP server for Neovim integration

Learn more at [maquina.app/documentation/ai-tools](https://maquina.app/documentation/ai-tools/).

